metadata.name: Lori Grace Miss Metaverse #1
metadata.description: Miss Metaverse (MM) is a limited randomly generated NFT collection of Matryoshka dolls, no two are alike. Gathered from every corner of the globe, these beautiful ladies will compete for the glorious title of Miss Metaverse. The Miss Metaverse Community honors and thanks Lori Grace for her contribution in creating a better society. Lori is a strong but humble Hispanic transwoman, dedicating much of her time to elevating artists by prolifically hosting “Women in NFT” Twitter Spaces focused on supporting and onboarding women, LGBTQI and other marginalized groups into the NFT space. Lori’s stunning art can be found on Foundation, OpenSea and https://www.lorigraceaz.com/. Lori, We wish you continued strength and success in your professional life and in helping the people who seek your guidance and support.
